default&#xa0;defaultPdefaultowers to stop, question and searchdefault&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
default“
defaultSchedule 7 powers are to be used solely for the pu
defaultrpose of 
defaultallowing for the determination of 
defaultwhether
default the
default person 
defaultexamined 
defaultappears to be
default, or to have been, concerned in 
defaultthe commission,
default 
defaultpreparation or instigation of acts of terrorism.  
defaultThe powers must not be used to stop and question persons for any other purpose.”
default 
default&#xa0;
defaultThe courts will no doubt continue, if necessary, to declare an examination unlawful on the basis that it was not used for the statutory purpose.
